---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
import Schedule from '../../components/Schedule';
---

<Base title="No-Gi" description="No-Gi submission grappling classes at Lions MMA Vancouver. Led by Guilherme Falcao, Gabrielle Stan, and Merck Milne.">

  <!-- Full-width hero image with text overlay -->
  <div class="relative w-full h-[280px] md:h-[520px] overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Image placeholder (swap for real <img> when photos arrive) -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-iron/60 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-3">
      <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-smoke/20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M23 19a2 2 0 01-2 2H3a2 2 0 01-2-2V8a2 2 0 012-2h4l2-3h6l2 3h4a2 2 0 012 2v11z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/><circle cx="12" cy="13" r="4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/></svg>
      <p class="font-mono text-[10px] tracking-widest text-smoke/30 uppercase">Image Coming Soon</p>
    </div>
    <!-- Dark overlay so text is readable -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-void/50"></div>
    <!-- Nav spacer + text pinned to bottom-left -->
    <div class="relative z-10 h-full flex flex-col justify-end pb-14 px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-20 max-w-7xl mx-auto w-full" style="padding-top: 96px;">
      <p class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-canvas/60 mb-4">SUBMISSION GRAPPLING</p>
      <h1 class="font-display text-[clamp(3.5rem,7vw,7rem)] uppercase tracking-tight text-canvas leading-none">NO-GI.</h1>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Content -->
  <div class="py-24 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">

    <!-- What it is -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 mb-24">
      <div>
        <p class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-smoke border-b border-iron pb-2 mb-8">WHAT IT IS</p>
        <div class="space-y-6 font-body text-canvas/80 leading-relaxed">
          <p>No-Gi is BJJ without the kimono. No collar grips, no lapel controls, no sleeve hooks. You are working with underhooks, overhooks, body locks, and wrist control. The absence of the Gi changes the pace, the grip game, and the submission entries significantly. Matches move faster. Wrestling becomes more central. The margin for sloppy technique gets thinner.</p>
          <p>The format has exploded in popularity over the last decade largely due to ADCC and EBI-style submission-only competition, and increasingly shows up as the dominant grappling format in MMA preparation. If you compete in Gi, No-Gi rounds out your game. If you train MMA, No-Gi is the more directly applicable format.</p>
          <p>At Lions, the No-Gi program is run by Guilherme Falcao, Gabrielle Stan, and Merck Milne. The instruction is technically grounded, not just scramble-heavy wrestling with submission attempts thrown in, but a coherent system of position, control, and finishing. Students build structured attacks from the guard, half guard, back, and leg entanglements.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
        <div class="flex-1 min-h-52 bg-iron/30 border border-iron flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-3">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-smoke/30" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M23 19a2 2 0 01-2 2H3a2 2 0 01-2-2V8a2 2 0 012-2h4l2-3h6l2 3h4a2 2 0 012 2v11z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/><circle cx="12" cy="13" r="4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/></svg>
          <p class="font-mono text-[10px] tracking-widest text-smoke/40 uppercase">Image Coming Soon</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1 min-h-52 bg-iron/30 border border-iron flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-3">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-smoke/30" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M23 19a2 2 0 01-2 2H3a2 2 0 01-2-2V8a2 2 0 012-2h4l2-3h6l2 3h4a2 2 0 012 2v11z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/><circle cx="12" cy="13" r="4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/></svg>
          <p class="font-mono text-[10px] tracking-widest text-smoke/40 uppercase">Image Coming Soon</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Who it is for -->
    <div class="mb-20 max-w-4xl">
      <p class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-smoke border-b border-iron pb-2 mb-8">WHO IT IS FOR</p>
      <ul class="space-y-3 font-body text-canvas/80 leading-relaxed">
        <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-brass font-mono text-xs mt-1 shrink-0">+</span><span>Gi BJJ practitioners who want to cross-train and remove the crutch of fabric grips</span></li>
        <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-brass font-mono text-xs mt-1 shrink-0">+</span><span>Wrestlers adding a submission layer to their existing game</span></li>
        <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-brass font-mono text-xs mt-1 shrink-0">+</span><span>MMA athletes training for realistic grappling situations</span></li>
        <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-brass font-mono text-xs mt-1 shrink-0">+</span><span>Competitors targeting ADCC-style or submission-only events</span></li>
        <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-brass font-mono text-xs mt-1 shrink-0">+</span><span>Anyone who wants a fast-paced, physically demanding grappling practice</span></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- 3-image gallery strip -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-24">
      {[1,2,3].map(() => (
        <div class="h-56 bg-iron/30 border border-iron flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-3">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-smoke/30" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M23 19a2 2 0 01-2 2H3a2 2 0 01-2-2V8a2 2 0 012-2h4l2-3h6l2 3h4a2 2 0 012 2v11z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/><circle cx="12" cy="13" r="4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/></svg>
          <p class="font-mono text-[10px] tracking-widest text-smoke/40 uppercase">Image Coming Soon</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <!-- What a class looks like -->
    <div class="mb-16 max-w-4xl">
      <p class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-smoke border-b border-iron pb-2 mb-8">WHAT A CLASS LOOKS LIKE</p>
      <p class="font-body text-canvas/80 leading-relaxed">No-Gi classes open with movement drills and level changes to get the body ready for wrestling-intensity movement. Technique instruction covers a specific position or attack chain, drilled with a partner at progressive resistance. Classes close with live rolling. The pace is higher than Gi classes on average. Expect to work harder for the same positional control, and to earn every submission you finish.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Wide image -->
    <div class="w-full h-64 bg-iron/30 border border-iron flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-3 mb-24">
      <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-smoke/30" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M23 19a2 2 0 01-2 2H3a2 2 0 01-2-2V8a2 2 0 012-2h4l2-3h6l2 3h4a2 2 0 012 2v11z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/><circle cx="12" cy="13" r="4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/></svg>
      <p class="font-mono text-[10px] tracking-widest text-smoke/40 uppercase">Image Coming Soon</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Schedule -->
    <div class="mb-16">
      <p class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-smoke border-b border-iron pb-2 mb-8">CLASS SCHEDULE</p>
      <Schedule client:load filterDiscipline="nogi" compact={true} />
    </div>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="border border-iron p-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center justify-between gap-6">
      <div>
        <p class="font-display text-2xl uppercase text-canvas">Try it free.</p>
        <p class="font-mono text-xs text-smoke mt-1">7 days. No commitment.</p>
      </div>
      <a href="/free-trial" class="inline-block bg-brass text-void font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase px-8 py-4 hover:bg-canvas transition-colors duration-200">
        CLAIM FREE TRIAL
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</Base>
